## ğŸ”„ FLOW DIAGRAM

### Login Success Flow
```
Input Credentials
      â†“
AuthContext.login()
      â†“
Validate role (admin/super_admin?)
      â†“
YES â†’ Save to localStorage
    â†’ Save currentUser
    â†’ setIsAuthenticated(true)
    â†’ Return success
    â†’ Navigate to /dashboard
```

### Protected Route Flow
```
User accesses /dashboard
      â†“
ProtectedRoute component
      â†“
Check isAuthenticated
      â†“
NO â†’ Redirect to /login
YES â†’ Check role
      â†“
NOT admin/super_admin â†’ Redirect to /login
YES â†’ Render component
```

